item.title: May 15, 2018 --- Quote of the Week: -------------- "The sign of a beautiful person is that they always see beauty in others."
I hope everyone took time to spoil the moms in their lives this past weekend and remembered all the moms that are no longer with us.
Spring Cleaning Time: Be sure to unplug the power to your modem for 2 minutes and then restart it. This will help with buffering issues.
